\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 While the full psychometric scales used in clinical trials are too lengthy for daily digital tracking, creating adapted short-form scales derived from these validated tools ensures that the consumer-facing platform maintains continuity with the rigorous scientific protocols.\
